                     <interp inst="t18440205-729-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> stealing 1 jar, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. and 3/4 <hi rend="italic">lb.</hi> weight of tobacco, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440205-name-1138" type="victimName">
