                     <hi rend="smallCaps">JOHN SHEARER</hi>
                  </persName>(<hi rend="italic">police constable H</hi> 154) I took Brown to the shop, and took Barry afterwards— I have known them both for eight or nine monthss— I have seen them more than once together.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined Q.</hi> Upon your solemn oath have you seen them together eight months ago? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I have seen them from one to nine months ago, in WHitechapel-road and about—Barry lives in Spring-gardens, Whitechapel.</p>
